    "description": "<p>Adepts of fist and bodily discipline, the Vowed are a partial Mage class dedicated to unarmed combat, physical training, and mental discipline. <strong>Vowed Benefits.</strong> Vowed are taken by an Adventurer with another partial class. Their hit dice can never be worse than 1d6 per level thanks to Martial Style. Each gains an appropriate non-combat bonus skill, such as Exert, Know, Pray, or Magic. Vowed do not cast spells but refine inner powers; these abilities cannot be used in heavy clothing, armor, or shields, though Armored Magic can mitigate this. At first level, a Vowed gains Martial Style, Unarmed Might, and Unarmored Defense, plus one additional ability.</p><h3>Partial Warrior/Vowed</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Hit Dice</th><th>Attack Bonus</th><th>Focus Picks</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>1d6+2</td><td>+1</td><td>1 Warrior, +1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>2d6+4</td><td>+2</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>3d6+6</td><td>+2</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>4d6+8</td><td>+3</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>5d6+10</td><td>+4</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>6d6+12</td><td>+5</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>7d6+14</td><td>+5</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>8d6+16</td><td>+6</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>9d6+18</td><td>+6</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>10d6+20</td><td>+7</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Partial Expert/Vowed</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Hit Dice</th><th>Attack Bonus</th><th>Focus Picks</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>1d6</td><td>+0</td><td>1 Expert, +1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>2d6</td><td>+1</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>3d6</td><td>+1</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>4d6</td><td>+2</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>5d6</td><td>+2</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>6d6</td><td>+3</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>7d6</td><td>+3</td><td>+1 Any</td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>8d6</td><td>+4</t